3D Scene Instruction Manual
Default Projection Mode is Perspective

################################
####        To build        ####
################################


    1. extract the folder fps_project from the fps_project.zip
    2. run ~$ make && ./fps_project

################################
####        Gameplay        ####
################################

////////// OBJECTIVE //////////
Beat the High Score


//////////// STATS ///////////////
Your Ammo is shown as "Ammo: (amount in gun) / (backup ammo)" in the bottom left
Your HitPoints (Health) is shown as "HP: |||||||||||||||" The number of bars is how much life you have left
Your score and the high score are in the TOP left
The Hobo's HitPoints are shown in the Top Middle


////////// POINTS //////////////
Collect AutoKill (red box)      =  1000
Collect Ammo Box (brown box)    =  400
Kill Hobo                       =  100


################################
####        Controls        ####
################################

MOVEMENT
W-A-S-D

LOOK AROUND
Move Mouse

SHOOT
left click

RELOAD
R

MELEE ATTACK (when enemy's close)
C

AUTOKILL (when you pick up green box)
G

JUMP
SpaceBar


/////// LIGHT CONTROL ////////

Move light forward/backward
    G/g and B/b keys

Change elevation up and down
    e and E keys

/////////////////////////////////////////



Close the window
    ESC key
    
Reset View
    '0' key

Zoom out/in
    'z'/'x' keys


